Ralden.

05:49.924 --> 05:52.508
Look, Alan, I know you're
suspicious of her,

05:52.510 --> 05:54.326
but she really makes me happy.

05:54.328 --> 05:56.178
No, I-I totally get that,
and, you know,

05:56.180 --> 05:57.796
I don't want
to sound judgmental,

05:57.798 --> 06:00.299
