06:19.019 --> 06:20.619
Oh, that's my cell.

06:20.621 --> 06:22.788
Could you grab it for me?

06:22.790 --> 06:25.049
It says "Do not answer."

06:25.050 --> 06:28.418
That's Zoey.

06:28.420 --> 06:30.937
It reminds me to stay strong
and not take her calls.

06:30.939 --> 06:31.988
Hello.

06:31.990 --> 06:34.290
Hey, Zoey.

06:34.292 --> 06:37.160
What's going on?

06:37.162 --> 06:38.578
Uh, yeah,

06:38.580 --> 06:39.829
I could do that.

06:39.831 --> 06:41.564
She wants to go for coffee.

06:41.566 --> 06:42.899
Why?
I don't know.

06:42.901 --> 06:44.668
Ask her.

06:44.670 --> 06:49.289
Hey, uh, just so I have
a heads up, is this a...

06:49.291 --> 06:53.393
sad coffee or a happy coffee?

06:53.395 --> 06:54.794
It's a happy coffee.

06:54.796 --> 06:58.431
Great. Can you bring
me back a scone?

06:58.433 --> 07:00.684
Shut up.

07:00.686 --> 07:04.270
Uh, yeah, great,
I'll be there in 20.

07:04.272 --> 07:05.755
Okay.

07:05.757 --> 07:07.207
So what do you think's going on?

07:07.209 --> 07:08.441
I don't know. Uh,

07:08.443 --> 07:11.061
she, she said she wants
to talk in person.

07:11.063 --> 07:13.196
Ooh, be careful-- in my
experience, when an ex wants

07:13.198 --> 07:15.365
to talk in person,
it's either to borrow money

07:15.367 --> 07:17.650
or tell you she gave you crabs.

07:19.136 --> 07:21.938
And no one's ever
asked me for money.

07:21.940 --> 07:24.858
You share too much.

07:24.860 --> 07:27.577
Besides, she said
it was a happy coffee.

07:27.579 --> 07:28.578
Ooh, ooh!

07:28.580 --> 07:30.463
Maybe she wants
to have sex with the ex.

07:30.465 --> 07:31.664
That's happened to me.

07:31.666 --> 07:33.950
Be careful, that's how
I got the crabs.

07:33.952 --> 07:36.970
Well, I'm not going
to sleep with her.

07:36.972 --> 07:38.722
I'm with Rose now.
Right.

07:38.724 --> 07:41.191
Oh, are you gonna tell Rose that
you're meeting Zoey for coffee?

07:41.193 --> 07:43.292
Yes, I am not.

07:43.294 --> 07:45.395
Good call.

07:45.397 --> 07:46.496
Hey, how do I look?

07:46.498 --> 07:48.732
