08:03.914 --> 08:06.116
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

08:06.118 --> 08:07.316
Here we go.

08:07.318 --> 08:08.868
Happy coffee.

08:08.870 --> 08:11.237
Thank you.

08:11.239 --> 08:12.405
So, how have you been?

08:12.407 --> 08:14.424
Mmm, good. You?

08:14.426 --> 08:17.160
Good.
Good.

08:17.162 --> 08:18.211
Are we done lying?

08:18.213 --> 08:19.629
Mm-hmm.

08:19.631 --> 08:21.831
Okay, so here it is.

08:21.833 --> 08:24.667
Oh, God, this is
very embarrassing.

08:24.669 --> 08:26.519
Crabs?

08:30.691 --> 08:32.142
What?

08:32.144 --> 08:34.027
Nothing. Go on.

08:34.029 --> 08:38.398
So, when you asked me
to marry you...

08:38.400 --> 08:40.683
it scared me.

08:40.684 --> 08:41.934
Why?

08:41.937 --> 08:44.120
I went down that
road before, Walden.

08:44.121 --> 08:45.655
I got lost.

08:46.957 --> 08:49.909
Just wasn't ready to make
that kind of commitment again.

08:49.911 --> 08:52.312
Wait a second.

08:52.314 --> 08:53.880
What about the other guy?

08:53.882 --> 08:54.964
Pe-ter.

08:54.966 --> 08:58.334
I broke up with him.

08:58.336 --> 09:00.837
So sorry.

09:00.839 --> 09:03.089
Oops, apparently
I'm not done lying.

09:03.091 --> 09:07.177
You care to know why
I broke up with Peter?

09:07.179 --> 09:09.679
Because he wasn't
a very good pumpkin eater?

09:13.517 --> 09:17.070
No, I broke up with him
because when I was with him,

09:17.072 --> 09:19.239
all I could think
about was you.

09:19.241 --> 09:23.576
Oh, this is a very happy coffee.

09:23.578 --> 09:27.013
I'd like another chance, Walden.

09:27.015 --> 09:29.899
My coffee is dancing.

09:29.901 --> 09:34.320
So, do you want to try
and make this work?

09:34.322 --> 09:36.923
I do.

09:36.925 --> 09:38.208
But it's a little complicated.

09:38.210 --> 09:39.676
Oh, God, you're seeing
someone, aren't you?

09:39.678 --> 09:40.910
Well...

09:40.912 --> 09:42.962
Is it serious?

09:42.964 --> 09:46.582
Nobody's brought
their toothbrush over.

09:46.584 --> 09:49.802
I'm sorry, I've put you
in a very awkward position.

09:49.804 --> 09:51.304
No, no, it's okay.

09:51.306 --> 09:55.191
I just... I need a little time
to figure it out.

09:55.193 --> 09:56.643
Of course you do.
I completely understand.

09:56.645 --> 09:58.061
Take all the time you need.

09:59.196 --> 10:00.930
You decided yet?

10:02.032 --> 10:04.033
I'm kidding.

10:04.035 --> 10:05.652
Look, do what you need to do

10:05.654 --> 10:07.770
and let me know
what happens, okay?

10:10.207 --> 10:11.991
Um...
Thanks for meeting me.

10:11.993 --> 10:14.327
Yeah, I'm glad you called.

10:20.134 --> 10:22.051
Oh, boy.

10:22.053 --> 10:24.304
Crabs would've been simpler.

10:25.506 --> 10:28.341
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

10:28.343 --> 10:30.410
You're not gonna believe this.

10:30.412 --> 10:33.313
Zoey realized she made
a huge mistake,

10:33.315 --> 10:34.597
and she wants me back.

10:34.599 --> 10:36.299
Is that crazy or what?

10:36.301 --> 10:38.051
No.

10:38.053 --> 10:39.052
No?

10:39.054 --> 10:40.136
Follow me.

10:40.138 --> 10:41.637
I want to show you something.

10:48.812 --> 10:50.096
Rose?

10:50.098 --> 10:52.332
Oh, hi, sweetie.

10:52.334 --> 10:55.201
I brought my toothbrush.

10:55.203 --> 10:58.454
That's crazy.

10:58.456 --> 11:00.757
