11:06.937 --> 11:08.337
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

11:08.339 --> 11:10.589
So,

11:10.591 --> 11:12.925
you decided to move in.

11:12.927 --> 11:14.426
Yep.

11:14.428 --> 11:16.461
You make me so happy.

11:16.463 --> 11:18.847
Now we never have
to be apart.

11:18.849 --> 11:19.982
Never?

11:19.984 --> 11:22.317
Never, ever.

11:23.470 --> 11:26.137
Now, if you'll excuse me,

11:26.139 --> 11:29.307
I'm going to go upstairs and
make sure the birds are settled.

11:31.161 --> 11:32.945
Great.

11:32.947 --> 11:35.914
Never, ever, ever.

11:37.867 --> 11:39.401
Did she say birds?

11:39.403 --> 11:40.869
Well, I counted four,

11:40.871 --> 11:44.439
but one of them might be dinner
for the ferrets.

11:44.441 --> 11:46.458
Ferrets?

11:46.460 --> 11:47.793
I think they were ferrets.

11:47.795 --> 11:48.961
Might've been weasels.

11:48.963 --> 11:50.379
Either way,

11:50.381 --> 11:52.497
she recommended
we all get rabies shots.

11:52.499 --> 11:55.184
Oh, God,

11:55.186 --> 11:56.418
what have I done?

11:56.420 --> 11:58.337
You asked her to move in.

11:58.339 --> 12:00.722
You invited the vampire
into the house.

12:00.724 --> 12:04.610
In my defense, the vampire
was naked at the time.

12:04.612 --> 12:07.012
So what are you going to do now?
I don't know.

12:07.014 --> 12:08.614
I guess I'll just...

12:08.616 --> 12:11.366
man up and tell Rose
I made a mistake.

12:11.368 --> 12:12.818
Ooh, that's a bad idea.

12:14.120 --> 12:16.154
Especially before you
get the rabies shot.

12:16.156 --> 12:17.789
You got a better one?

12:17.791 --> 12:19.825
Well, let's see, um,
you could always tell her

12:19.827 --> 12:21.410
that your, your work
is taking you

12:21.412 --> 12:23.328
to Europe or that you're dying

12:23.330 --> 12:25.330
or that you finally realized
you're gay

12:25.332 --> 12:28.333
and you're sick of fighting
the feelings you have for me.

12:32.422 --> 12:34.456
I'm not gonna lie to her.

12:34.458 --> 12:36.141
Would it be a lie?

12:40.230 --> 12:42.147
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

12:42.149 --> 12:44.215
Look at us.

12:44.217 --> 12:45.400
We're like Siamese twins

12:45.402 --> 12:47.853
except we don't have
to share any organs,

12:47.855 --> 12:50.155
unless we want to.

12:51.942 --> 12:53.859
Listen,

12:53.861 --> 12:57.863
I need to talk to
you about something.

12:57.865 --> 13:00.148
Sure.

13:00.150 --> 13:03.185
Geez, this is tough.

13:03.187 --> 13:04.453
Just say it.

13:04.455 --> 13:07.039
I want us to be able
to talk about anything.

13:08.958 --> 13:11.226
Okay, here goes.

13:11.228 --> 13:13.712
Um...

13:15.247 --> 13:17.232
I'm in love with Alan.

13:17.234 --> 13:18.417
What?

13:18.419 --> 13:19.351
I'm dying.

13:19.353 --> 13:20.535
You're dying?

13:20.537 --> 13:22.437
For work. In Europe.

13:22.439 --> 13:25.423
Walden,

13:25.425 --> 13:27.592
what is going on?

13:29.028 --> 13:31.897
Okay, um...

13:33.766 --> 13:37.786
