13:56.206 --> 13:59.174
Are you still in love
with her?

14:01.627 --> 14:04.012
Yes, I am.

14:05.898 --> 14:08.150
I'm sorry, Rose.

14:11.521 --> 14:14.356
No.

14:14.358 --> 14:17.743
No, don't be sorry.

14:19.112 --> 14:21.029
Walden, we've only known
each other

14:21.031 --> 14:24.416
for a couple of weeks.

14:24.418 --> 14:26.184
And as wonderful
as it's been,

14:26.186 --> 14:28.337
if you feel that you'd be
happier with Zoey,

14:28.339 --> 14:31.707
I'm not gonna stand
in your way.

14:33.126 --> 14:35.326
Thank you.

14:37.764 --> 14:40.716
How did you know
her name is Zoey?

14:42.135 --> 14:45.270
Zoey's a very popular name
in England.

14:45.272 --> 14:47.990
Wait, how did you
know she's English?

14:47.992 --> 14:50.642
Because her name's
Zoey, silly.

14:53.529 --> 14:55.313
Good-bye, Walden.

14:57.033 --> 14:59.517
Good-bye, Rose.

14:59.519 --> 15:03.689
You know I want you
to be happy, don't you?

15:03.691 --> 15:05.741
I do,

15:05.743 --> 15:07.926
and I want you to be happy, too.

15:07.928 --> 15:10.629
Thank you.

