I got a promotion.

15:29.299 --> 15:31.233
No kidding.

15:31.235 --> 15:33.518
Yep. I'm the dessert chef
in the officer's mess.

15:33.520 --> 15:34.553
Wow.

15:34.555 --> 15:36.221
Yeah, I made
this killer crème brûlée

15:36.223 --> 15:38.140
for the enlisted guys
and word got out.

15:38.142 --> 15:40.442
Jake, I am so proud of you.

15:40.444 --> 15:42.244
Yeah, they gave me
my own blow torch.

15:42.246 --> 15:43.745
You know,
to caramelize the sugar.

15:43.747 --> 15:45.197
Check it out.

15:47.201 --> 15:48.283
Uh-oh.

15:48.285 --> 15:51.169
Not again.

15:51.171 --> 15:52.737
Got to go, Dad.

15:56.876 --> 15:59.878
Well,
he's America's problem now.

15:59.880 --> 16:01.963
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

16:05.351 --> 16:07.752
Hi.

16:07.754 --> 16:10.421
Hello?

16:10.423 --> 16:11.606
Sorry to bother you.

16:11.608 --> 16:13.008
I'm a friend of Walden's.

16:13.010 --> 16:14.876
Oh, really?

16:14.878 --> 16:18.263
Yes, and we need to talk.

16:18.265 --> 16:20.065
About what?

16:20.917 --> 16:23.601
It's complicated.

16:25.555 --> 16:27.989
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

16:29.209 --> 16:30.441
I'll get it.

16:37.617 --> 16:38.633
Zoey?

16:38.635 --> 16:39.668
Who the hell is...

16:39.670 --> 16:40.919
What has happened
to your face?

16:40.921 --> 16:42.771
I was attacked by ferrets.

16:42.773 --> 16:45.590
Fine, don't tell me.

16:45.592 --> 16:47.759
Who the hell
is that crazy woman

16:47.761 --> 16:50.595
who just showed up at my house
saying she's carrying your baby?

16:50.597 --> 16:51.963
Uh...

16:51.965 --> 16:53.365
I have a guess.

16:53.367 --> 16:56.301
Alan, please.

16:56.303 --> 16:57.602
Do you know anything
about this?

16:57.604 --> 16:59.738
All right, I'm just
gonna level with you.

16:59.740 --> 17:03.241
You moved on, so I was trying
to do the same thing,

17:03.243 --> 17:04.542
but she's not pregnant.

17:04.545 --> 17:06.310
Then, why in the world
would she show up

17:06.313 --> 17:08.079
at my apartment
claiming to be?

17:08.080 --> 17:09.314
Apparently she is crazy.

17:09.316 --> 17:10.982
Told you.
Alan!

17:11.817 --> 17:13.084
Shut up!

17:16.105 --> 17:17.672
All right, look,

17:17.674 --> 17:20.842
as soon as you told me that
you wanted to get back together,

17:20.844 --> 17:24.162
I told her she had to move out
because I was in love with you.

17:24.164 --> 17:25.747
And that's the truth.

17:25.749 --> 17:27.265
I love you, Zoey.

17:27.267 --> 17:29.100
Wait, she was living here?

17:29.102 --> 17:31.386
Did you hear the part
where I said I love you?

17:31.388 --> 17:34.873
What happened to "no one's
brought their toothbrush"?

17:34.875 --> 17:36.091
That...

17:36.093 --> 17:37.192
Alan?

17:37.194 --> 17:38.593
You told me to shut up.

17:38.595 --> 17:40.345
God.

17:40.347 --> 17:41.980
Good-bye, Walden.

17:41.982 --> 17:45.200
Zoey, wait, you're
my stinky cheese!

17:48.354 --> 17:50.121
Great.

17:50.123 --> 17:53.024
Aw, I'm sorry, buddy.

17:53.026 --> 17:56.278
But look at the bright side...

17:56.280 --> 17:58.696
I know, I still have you.

17:58.698 --> 18:01.766
For ever and ever and ever.

18:03.369 --> 18:05.804
Hey, why don't we go out?

18:05.806 --> 18:07.389
You know,
maybe-maybe grab a bite?

18:07.391 --> 18:08.690
That might cheer you up.

18:08.692 --> 18:09.624
I don't want to go out.

18:09.626 --> 18:10.759
Come on, you have to eat.

18:10.761 --> 18:12.510
You want me to pick something up
for you?

18:12.512 --> 18:13.762
Fine.

18:13.764 --> 18:15.230
Great, great, uh,
oh, so listen, uh...

18:15.232 --> 18:16.598
Here you go.
Thanks.

18:16.600 --> 18:18.767
Oh, uh, would you mind
if I take your car?

18:18.769 --> 18:19.851
Mine's...
Out of gas.

18:19.853 --> 18:21.386
Sure.

18:23.640 --> 18:24.889
Berta's right.

18:24.891 --> 18:26.724
I am the master.

18:31.831 --> 18:33.331
Oh, boy,

18:33.333 --> 18:35.533
a radio and brakes.

18:40.624 --> 18:42.507
Oh, yeah.

18:42.509 --> 18:44.793
I could get used to this.

18:47.598 --> 18:49.381
Not the face!

18:49.383 --> 18:51.883
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪
Not the face!

18:58.147 --> 18:59.964
♪ <i>Men.</i> ♪

19:03.652 --> 19:05.403
I've made a decision.

19:05.405 --> 19:06.604
What's that?

19:06.606 --> 19:09.925
I'm never going to care
about another human being.

19:09.926 --> 19:11.726
Ouch.

19:11.728 --> 19:13.327
Except you.

19:13.329 --> 19:14.862
That's better.

19:14.864 --> 19:17.698
I can't believe
I lost Zoey again.

19:17.700 --> 19:21.169
I can't believe I lost
the tip of my pinky to a ferret.

19:21.171 --> 19:24.288
Boo-hoo. I have half a nipple.

19:25.425 --> 19:27.141
All right.

19:27.143 --> 19:28.426
Good night, Alan.

19:28.428 --> 19:30.628
Good night, Walden.

19:37.901 --> 19:39.669
Good night, Rose.

19:39.671 --> 19:41.037
Good night, Alan.

